headline: McLaren Racing CEO talks F1 growth, Netflix, Big Tech sponsors
summary: McLaren Racing CEO Zak Brown sits down with Market Catalysts anchor Julie Hyman and Yahoo Finance senior autos reporter Pras Subramanian to discuss the surge in popularity of Formula One (FWONK), valuation growth, the impact of Netflix's Drive to Survive series (NFLX), and the role of Big Tech companies in corporate sponsorships. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Catalysts.
